text: Goephanes basiflavicornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1966.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1966 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
